attributes.Long form description: The instructor says, "please assemble this chair."The student assembles the legs, and then he assembles the seat. After that, he screws the first, the second, the third, and the fourth screw. Finally he tightens the middle screw.

attributes.Transcription: We are now going to assemble the small IKEA chair Marius.
So please go ahead and assemble it.
So actually, assemble the legs first.
Try the edges in small amounts.
